info.author: Andrew Smiley
info.description: BetterCSV provides the tools for parsing CSV that are lacking in the Python language itself. Use BetterCSV to read CSV files in as lists, dictionaries with column header keys,etc. Use BetterCSV to write to CSV, compare files, etc.
